tering experiments as a function of field and\ntemperature, giving us the opportunity to identify existing excitation branches\nin CeB6 and conclusively compare them with the theoretically predicted\nmultipolar excitations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 13:17:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-13"}
