ur thus far and we show that more data of the variables\nalready monitored would not result in higher predictive accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 15:17:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 09:50:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 12:34:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-01"}
