uture recurrence of the\nepidemic, while avoiding saturation of the regional health systems and\nmitigating impact on costs. Our study and methodology can be easily extended to\nother levels of granularity (provinces or counties in the same region or states\nin other federal countries, etc.) to support policy- and decision-makers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 15:30:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-18"}
